      "description": "Honest poor-condition project vehicle being sold as-is. It shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, with noticeable aging, blemishes, and overall signs of hard use. Buyers should expect mechanical issues, deferred maintenance, and the likelihood that it will need significant repair work before it can be considered a dependable driver. Best suited for someone looking for a restoration project, budget fixer-upper, or parts donor rather than a clean, ready-to-go example.",
