    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition example that presents nicely overall. The exterior shows well with a clean appearance, though buyers should expect some normal age-related cosmetic wear and small imperfections consistent with use. The interior is in good shape for its age, appearing complete and cared for, and the vehicle should make a solid driver for someone wanting a nice example without paying top-of-market mint-condition money. Overall, this is an honest, good-quality car that looks respectable and should meet expectations for a properly maintained used vehicle.",
