    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. A practical choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or someone looking for an affordable project, it delivers strong value for the money and a chance to own for far less than newer alternatives. If you want simple, honest transportation without stretching your budget, this is well worth a look.",
