    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right owner? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a handy runabout, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s being priced fairly and presented honestly, with the kind of straightforward sale you can feel good about. If you want inexpensive motoring without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
