      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running driver with plenty of life left in the powertrain and a solid platform for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. Starts, moves, and stops, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels usable for daily duty or as a budget project. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. Great opportunity to get into an affordable car with good bones, straightforward mechanicals, and room to improve over time.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
